  <summary date="2023-07-19T18:49:38Z" status="Introduced in House">90-Day Review Act

This bill reduces the time limit to file a petition for judicial review of a federal permit, license, or approval for a highway or public transportation capital project. Specifically, the bill reduces the current 150-day time limit to 90 days.</summary>
